---
import { Image } from "astro:assets";
import scienceImage from "../assets/figma-import/hero-dashboard.png";
---

<section class="relative overflow-hidden py-20 md:py-24">

  <div class="section-shell">
    <div class="grid gap-12 lg:grid-cols-2 lg:items-center">
      <!-- Left content -->
      <div class="space-y-6 ">
        <p class="font-display text-lg md:text-2xl text-[#09cc9c] font-medium">The Science</p>
        <h2 class="font-display text-5xl md:text-6xl font-bold leading-tight">
          Backed by seven sciences.<br />Validated by decades of research.
        </h2>
        <p class="text-lg leading-relaxed">
          Stanford. Harvard Business School. Gallup. University of Michigan. The frameworks behind Zorakle don't come from a single proprietary algorithm — they come from the most validated work in psychology, organizational behavior, and performance science. We integrate seven of them. That's why Zorakle predicts what others can't.
        </p>
      </div>

      <!-- Right: Image placeholder -->
      <div class="rounded-3xl overflow-hidden shadow-2xl border border-white/20">
        <div class="relative aspect-video bg-gradient-to-br from-[#1a5f52] to-[#0d8b78] flex items-center justify-center">
          <Image
            src={scienceImage}
            alt="Zorakle science dashboard"
            class="w-full h-full object-cover"
          />
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

